Description: A statistical model for assessing reproducibility in replicate 
    Hi-C data. SIDR extends the standard irreproducible discovery rate 
    framework by stratifying Hi-C interactions according to genomic distance, 
    accommodating structured heterogeneity in replicate consistency. 
